photo.title: It's another year.

description._content:
Celebrating a birthday at the posh St. Regis Hotel in San Francisco, Ca. (I took this 2 yrs ago when taking pictures were more of just casual snaphsots here & there☺)

One of the best, most luxurious hotels I've stayed at. Worth the $500/night price tag  -- loved it so much that I became a return guest right before the year ended.☺
